  <brief_title>Omepral速 Tablets Special Clinical Experience Investigation in Patients With Erosive Esophagitis</brief_title>
  <acronym>OMAREE</acronym>
  <official_title>Omepral速 Tablets Mega-study to Investigate the Efficacy on Various Type of Acid Reflux Related Symptoms and QOL, and Epidemiology in Patients With Erosive Esophagitis in Daily Medical Practice</official_title>
  <sponsors>
