  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This open label, non-interventional study is to compare the efficacy of Omepral速 tablet and
      any other treatments excepting proton pump inhibitors (PPIs) for the treatment of various
      type of acid reflux related symptoms in patients with reflux esophagitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
